{"tid":2376840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大被捕女子向警署寄感謝卡　盛讚囚室生活「有4.5分」","createTime":"2021-01-23T06:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T07:51:34.000Z","uid":271829,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9430194fd7807ec402947e88f996a2e562457a13","tid":2376840,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/1PKChk69_DnwZaEM8OhaU1-6c4U=/2047x1152/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FHXQ24ZSSVGV5ITSVCN2OMBIWE.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1PKChk69_DnwZaEM8OhaU1-6c4U%3D%2F2047x1152%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFHXQ24ZSSVGV5ITSVCN2OMBIWE.jpeg&h=32e68c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在自製感謝卡上，特別提到四名辛勤的獄警，指他們為了照顧倉內囚犯，做了很多不為人知的事情。圖片來源 : Twitter/West Shore RCMP @WestshoreRCMP<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n加拿大一名女子，上周被皇家騎警拘捕後，在警署內被扣押數日後獲釋，回家後特意向獄警寄出自製感謝卡，感謝連日悉心照顧，更指如果滿分為五分，囚室內生活環境她會給予4.5分。事件引來美國名嘴吉米法倫（Jimmy Fallon）關注，在脫口秀中稱「這很可能是『最加拿大人』（most Candaian）的事情。」<br />\n該張自製感謝卡上，特別提到四名辛勤的獄警，指他們為了照顧囚犯，做了很多不為人知的事情。感謝卡首頁有摺紙飛機和多件行李的圖案，並寫着「若果我們在飛機遇上問題，我會先幫你帶上氧氣罩，之後才會調整自己的（氧氣罩）。」（If, for some reason, our airplane was experiencing problems, I would help you with your oxygen mask before adjusting mine.&rdquo;），以表達對獄警的感激。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210123/C33G5V7SMNFWHMDIKUFHVDLUWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210123%2FC33G5V7SMNFWHMDIKUFHVDLUWE%2F&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5PaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=661ddaee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210123%2FC33G5V7SMNFWHMDIKUFHVDLUWE%2F&h=35d82c86\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210123/C33G5V7SMNFWHMDIKUFHVDLUWE/</a>"},{"pid":"b6c82b47647b48d6197462dbe221f5